name: firstSketch (2021)
description: My genesis work on H=N is one of the first digital art pieces I created, inspired by a grid tunnel. The title contains a reference to every program scripted in Processing, a software I've found while exploring new media art in the NFT world. Then it becomes the tool of choice that produced the final ("image.jpg") for my profile pic at my long-gone Twitter account @_sqarpa_.
